# Kigrama Fuel Station Management System
## AI-Enhanced MVP Project Description

### ðŸŽ¯ **Project Overview**
A comprehensive, AI-powered fuel station management system built with **Vue.js 3**, **Metronic 8**, and **TrailBase** that delivers enterprise-grade functionality through a single responsive codebase serving both web and mobile platforms. The system focuses on operational excellence, regulatory compliance, and intelligent automation for fuel retail operations across Uganda.

---

## ðŸš€ **Core MVP Features (Ship-it-Now)**

### **1. Authentication & RBAC Foundation**
- **Multi-level Role-Based Access Control** with 26+ predefined roles
- **JWT-based authentication** with TrailBase backend
- **Position-based permissions** integrated with organizational hierarchy
- **Mobile-responsive login** with biometric support (mobile)
- **Session management** with automatic token refresh

### **2. Station & Infrastructure Management**
- **Master Station Registry** with 13+ stations across Uganda
- **Tank & Pump Configuration** with real-time monitoring
- **Equipment Status Tracking** with maintenance schedules
- **Geographic Coverage** across Central, Eastern, and Western regions
- **Capacity Management** with automated alerts

### **3. Product & Pricing Intelligence**
- **Central Price-Book Management** for 18+ product types
- **Dynamic Pricing Engine** with approval workflows
- **Multi-tier Product Categories** (Fuel, Lubricants, Gas, Services)
- **Real-time Price Updates** across all stations
- **Tax Integration** with URA compliance (38+ tax types)

### **4. Smart Inventory & Reconciliation**
- **Real-time Wet-Stock Monitoring** with variance detection
- **AI-Powered Leak Detection** with immediate alerts
- **Automated Reorder Points** with supplier integration
- **Stock Movement Tracking** with full audit trails
- **Variance Dashboard** with actionable insights

### **5. POS & Transaction Processing**
- **Integrated Pump Control** with EMV/contactless payments
- **Age Verification System** for restricted products
- **Multi-payment Method Support** (Cash, Card, Mobile Money)
- **Real-time Transaction Logging** with fraud detection
- **Receipt Management** with digital options

### **6. Intelligent Approval Workflows**
- **7-Tier Approval Matrix** covering all money-moving operations:
  1. Purchase Orders (>$10,000 auto-escalates to CFO)
  2. Delivery Variances (>Â±2% requires manager approval)
  3. Stock Adjustments (>500L or $2,000 requires finance approval)
  4. Inter-station Transfers (dual approval required)
  5. Price Changes (CFO approval required)
  6. Shift Variances (manager sign-off required)
  7. Ledger Corrections (finance controller approval)
- **24-hour SLA Management** with auto-escalation
- **Mobile Approval Interface** for managers on-the-go

### **7. Financial Management & Compliance**
- **Double-Entry Ledger System** with automated GL posting
- **URA Tax Integration** with 38+ tax types and rates
- **VAT, PAYE, Excise Duty** automated calculations
- **Financial Reporting** with real-time dashboards
- **Audit Trail Maintenance** for regulatory compliance

### **8. HR & Workforce Management**
- **Employee Roster Management** with 220+ job grades
- **Clock-in/Clock-out System** with GPS verification
- **Performance Tracking** with review cycles
- **Succession Planning** with career path mapping
- **Leave Management** with automated accruals

### **9. Environmental & Compliance Monitoring**
- **UST Compliance Reporting** with automated submissions
- **Environmental Impact Tracking** with regulatory alerts
- **Safety Protocol Management** with incident reporting
- **Compliance Dashboard** with real-time status indicators

### **10. AI-Enhanced Features**
- **Predictive Analytics** for demand forecasting
- **Fraud Detection Engine** with machine learning
- **Anomaly Detection** for operational irregularities
- **Smart Notifications** with context-aware alerts
- **Performance Optimization** recommendations

