## ðŸ›  **Technical Architecture**

### **Frontend Stack**
- **Vue.js 3 Composition API** for reactive, maintainable code
- **Metronic 8 Premium** for enterprise-grade UI components
- **Responsive Design** with mobile-first approach
- **Progressive Web App (PWA)** capabilities for mobile deployment
- **TypeScript Integration** for type safety and better DX

### **Backend & Data**
- **TrailBase** as primary backend and database
- **RESTful API Architecture** with standardized endpoints
- **Real-time Data Sync** with WebSocket connections
- **Automated Backup Systems** with point-in-time recovery
- **Horizontal Scaling** capabilities for growth

### **Mobile Optimization**
- **Single Codebase Strategy** using Vue.js responsive design
- **Touch-Optimized Interfaces** with 44px+ touch targets
- **Offline Capability** with local data caching
- **Native-like Performance** through PWA optimization
- **Camera Integration** for receipt scanning and barcode reading

### **Security & Compliance**
- **End-to-End Encryption** for sensitive data
- **Role-Based Data Filtering** at API level
- **Audit Logging** for all user actions
- **GDPR Compliance** with data privacy controls
- **Regular Security Audits** with penetration testing

